<lyrics>[V1]
 Maw lawmhnak ni, Bawi Jesuh kha, Keimah ka biak ka zumhnak ni, A-tu
 keimah lung aa lawm ca, Mi sinah ka chim lai a si.

[C1]
   Lawmhnak ni, lawmhnak ni, Jesuh ka sual a tawlnak ni; Thlacamnak kha
   a ka cawnpiak, Ni-fa-te in a ka lawmhter, Lawmhnak ni, Lawmhnak ni, Jesuh
   ka sual a tawlnak ni.

[V2]
 A dih cang rian-pi a dih cang, Keimah cu Jesuh mi ka si, Jesuh
 authawng ka theih ka hung, A ka auh ca, lawmhnak tampi.

[C2]
   Lawmhnak ni, lawmhnak ni, Jesuh ka sual a tawlnak ni; Thlacamnak kha
   a ka cawnpiak, Ni-fa-te in a ka lawmhter, Lawmhnak ni, Lawmhnak ni, Jesuh
   ka sual a tawlnak ni.

[V3]
 Hnangam lo-in saupi ka um, Ka ra ko lai, hi umnak ah, Bawipa sinin i
 then hin hlah, A liannganbik Bawipa a si.

[C3]
   Lawmhnak ni, lawmhnak ni, Jesuh ka sual a tawlnak ni; Thlacamnak kha
   a ka cawnpiak, Ni-fa-te in a ka lawmhter, Lawmhnak ni, Lawmhnak ni, Jesuh
   ka sual a tawlnak ni.

[V4]
 Ka biakarnak Pathian theih cang, Nifate in ka kar than lai, A hnu bik
 ka thih caan tiangin, A ka dawt ca kaa lawm te lai.

[C4]
   Lawmhnak ni, lawmhnak ni, Jesuh ka sual a tawlnak ni; Thlacamnak kha
   a ka cawnpiak, Ni-fa-te in a ka lawmhter, Lawmhnak ni, Lawmhnak ni, Jesuh
   ka sual a tawlnak ni.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>MAW LAWMHNAK NI CH202</title>
</song>